<!-- FOUNDING NARRATIVE + STAT MOSAIC -->
<section class="founding-section section-pad">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="founding-grid">
      <div class="founding-content">
        <span class="label" data-i18n="founding-label">Our Story</span>
        <h2 class="display-lg reveal" data-i18n="founding-heading">Two decades of <em>evidence-led</em> advisory</h2>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1" data-i18n="founding-p1">
          North Sphere was founded in Ottawa in 2004 by a group of senior advisors who had spent careers inside the institutions they sought to improve — the UN, bilateral development agencies, federal ministries, and multilateral banks. They believed that the most effective advisory came from people who understood the political economy of reform from the inside.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2" data-i18n="founding-p2">
          Over twenty years, we have grown from a small team focused on health systems in Sub-Saharan Africa to a global practice spanning six domains and four continents. What has not changed is our commitment to rigour, independence, and the primacy of local context.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-3" data-i18n="founding-p3">
          Today, North Sphere operates through a hub-and-spoke model: a core permanent team of senior partners and directors, augmented by a carefully curated network of 80+ associate experts deployed based on the specific demands of each mandate.
        </p>

        <div class="founding-milestones reveal reveal-delay-4">
          <div class="milestone">
            <span class="milestone-year" data-i18n="ms-2004">2004</span>
            <div class="milestone-text">
              <strong data-i18n="ms-2004-title">Founded in Ottawa</strong>
              <span data-i18n="ms-2004-desc">Established as a health systems advisory firm serving USAID, DFID, and the World Bank.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone">
            <span class="milestone-year" data-i18n="ms-2010">2010</span>
            <div class="milestone-text">
              <strong data-i18n="ms-2010-title">Expanded to Six Domains</strong>
              <span data-i18n="ms-2010-desc">Broadened practice to include education, environment, and institutional development following demand from multilateral clients.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone">
            <span class="milestone-year" data-i18n="ms-2016">2016</span>
            <div class="milestone-text">
              <strong data-i18n="ms-2016-title">Opened Geneva &amp; Nairobi Offices</strong>
              <span data-i18n="ms-2016-desc">Established regional hubs to better serve European institutions and the African Union.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone">
            <span class="milestone-year" data-i18n="ms-2023">2023</span>
            <div class="milestone-text">
              <strong data-i18n="ms-2023-title">Asia-Pacific Practice Launched</strong>
              <span data-i18n="ms-2023-desc">New Singapore office anchors growing work across South and Southeast Asia.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
